        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[펠로시, 인도·태평양 지역 순방 시작…‘대만 방문’ 여부엔 함구]]></title>
            <link>https://www.khan.co.kr/world/world-general/article/202207312146035/?utm_campaign=list_click&amp;utm_source=reporter_article&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=%EB%B0%95%EC%9D%80%ED%95%98_%EA%B8%B0%EC%9E%90%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80</link>
